    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Creating arrays\n",
        "\n",
        "### Arrays created from lists and other array-like objects\n"
      ],
      "id": "0a546375"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([1, 2, 3, 4])\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "7a261d74",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array(((1, 2), (3, 4)))\n",
        "data.ndim, data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "ff205fa6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with constant values\n"
      ],
      "id": "681c503b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.zeros((2, 3))"
      ],
      "id": "ed7be61d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.ones(4)\n",
        "data, data.dtype"
      ],
      "id": "488635d4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "5.4 * np.ones(10)"
      ],
      "id": "a63877c6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.full(10, 5.4) # slightly more efficient"
      ],
      "id": "8af3a24b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x1 = np.empty(5)\n",
        "x1.fill(3.0)\n",
        "x1"
      ],
      "id": "b186b8a7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with incremental sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "31d8862e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.arange(0, 11, 1)"
      ],
      "id": "1e715d8c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.linspace(0, 10, 11)  # generally recommended"
      ],
      "id": "a9bb4f5b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Arrays filled with logarithmic sequences\n"
      ],
      "id": "058b3e37"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.logspace(0, 2, 10)  # 5 data points between 10**0=1 to 10**2=100"
      ],
      "id": "7477b105",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Mesh grid arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "c893607e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "x = np.array([-1, 0, 1])\n",
        "y = np.array([-2, 0, 2])\n",
        "\n",
        "X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y)"
      ],
      "id": "afd88f4d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "X"
      ],
      "id": "2242e25e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Y"
      ],
      "id": "58edff94",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "Z = (X + Y)**2\n",
        "Z"
      ],
      "id": "26765ae4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating uninitialized arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "437a13ce"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.empty(3, dtype=float)"
      ],
      "id": "911d1e5b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating arrays with properties of other arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "b99ac0ff"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "def f(x):    \n",
        "    y = np.ones_like(x)    # compute with x and y    \n",
        "    return y\n",
        "\n",
        "x = np.array([[1, 2, 3], [4, 5, 6]])\n",
        "y = f(x)\n",
        "y"
      ],
      "id": "b2dc28cd",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Creating matrix arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "bf174d83"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.identity(4)"
      ],
      "id": "637b0c5a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=1)"
      ],
      "id": "3f92b959",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.eye(4, k=-1)"
      ],
      "id": "fa39092f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "np.diag(np.arange(0, 20, 5))"
      ],
      "id": "1fff1f99",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Indexing and slicing\n",
        "\n",
        "### One-dimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "0738cae7"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a = np.arange(0, 11)\n",
        "a"
      ],
      "id": "3cc498ef",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[0]"
      ],
      "id": "5c20a454",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-1]"
      ],
      "id": "8f2c37e0",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[4]"
      ],
      "id": "0e6ca48f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "df86efb9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1]"
      ],
      "id": "3a2f11a4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[1:-1:2]"
      ],
      "id": "b83442db",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "edb47716"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[:5]"
      ],
      "id": "ab8a4041",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[-5:]"
      ],
      "id": "b55a04c9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "a[::-2]"
      ],
      "id": "5d119a89",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Multidimensional arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "ef9edc7d"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "f = lambda m, n: n + 10*m"
      ],
      "id": "6b072270",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "# please search for numpy.fromfunction at google\n",
        "A = np.fromfunction(f, (6, 6), dtype=int)\n",
        "A  "
      ],
      "id": "44751d69",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:, 1]  # the second column"
      ],
      "id": "bb724560",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1, :]  # the second row"
      ],
      "id": "a48707c4",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[:3, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "50ded580",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[3:, :3]"
      ],
      "id": "f231a032",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[::2, ::2]"
      ],
      "id": "527ad6a1",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[1::2, 1::3]"
      ],
      "id": "119f04ee",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Views\n",
        "\n",
        "* Subarrays that are extracted from arrays using slice operations are **alternative views** of the same underlying array data. That is, $~$they are arrays that refer to the same data in memory as the original array, $~$but with a different `strides` configuration\n",
        "\n",
        "* When elements in a view are assigned new values, $~$the values of the original\n",
        "array are therefore also updated. For example,\n"
      ],
      "id": "28950e7e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[1:5, 1:5]\n",
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "d1c820f3",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[:, :] = 0\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "0c1d5330",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* When a copy rather than a view is needed, the view can be copied explicitly by using the `copy` method of the `ndarray` instance\n"
      ],
      "id": "cf63c944"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C = B[1:3, 1:3].copy()\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "e80123c8",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "C[:, :] = 1\n",
        "C"
      ],
      "id": "049bbbf7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B"
      ],
      "id": "17b68651",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Fancy indexing and boolean-valued indexing\n"
      ],
      "id": "e0cb469f"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.linspace(0, 1, 11)\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "2cdb6b36",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[np.array([0, 2, 4])]"
      ],
      "id": "fa25810b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[[0, 2, 4]]"
      ],
      "id": "2c0c8d9c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "d52ac2da"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A > 0.5"
      ],
      "id": "228929ed",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 0.5]"
      ],
      "id": "acd9354c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* Unlike arrays created by using slices, $~$**the arrays returned using fancy indexing and Boolean-valued\n",
        "indexing are not views**, $~$but rather new independent arrays\n"
      ],
      "id": "80ef381b"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)\n",
        "indices = [2, 4, 6]"
      ],
      "id": "e9bafd90",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[indices]"
      ],
      "id": "37052070",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "f9640775",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[indices] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "b675c85f",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "2721a9de"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A = np.arange(10)"
      ],
      "id": "13acf4e5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B = A[A > 5]"
      ],
      "id": "23b86304",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "B[0] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "66a14535",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "A[A > 5] = -1\n",
        "A"
      ],
      "id": "b57441a5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "### Summery\n"
      ],
      "id": "b4d3d62e"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, :')"
      ],
      "id": "4eec0e36",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0')"
      ],
      "id": "d44be15e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1, :')"
      ],
      "id": "bf3114cb",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, 2')"
      ],
      "id": "8c7b9e42",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "bc2035f9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 0:2')"
      ],
      "id": "dadd677c",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '0:2, 2:4')"
      ],
      "id": "6a66fa5e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '::2, ::2')"
      ],
      "id": "113c046a",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1::2, 1::2')"
      ],
      "id": "284cc642",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "5a4d17cf",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '[1, 3], [0, 3]')"
      ],
      "id": "aa56a15e",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), ':, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "5755dd57",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "show_array((4, 4), '1:3, [False, True, True, False]')"
      ],
      "id": "dba1ba1b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "## Reshaping and resizing\n",
        "\n",
        "* Reshaping an array does not require modifying the underlying array data; it only changes in how the data is interpreted, by redefining the array’s strides attribute\n"
      ],
      "id": "a93236b9"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.reshape(data, (1, 4))\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "4162f882",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0, 1] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "1baac5a6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.reshape(4)\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "4584b2e2",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[1] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "24f31fe7",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "24547adb"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]])\n",
        "data1 = np.ravel(data)\n",
        "data1"
      ],
      "id": "804ed39d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data1[0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "321fbf1b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "* The `ndarray` method `flatten` perform the same function, $~$but\n",
        "returns a **copy** instead of a view\n"
      ],
      "id": "4a80e7a3"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2 = data.flatten()\n",
        "data2"
      ],
      "id": "73393c95",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data2[0] = -2\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "59667088",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "---\n"
      ],
      "id": "e09415fb"
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "data = np.arange(0, 5)\n",
        "data.shape"
      ],
      "id": "1f8153f6",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column = data[:, np.newaxis]\n",
        "column"
      ],
      "id": "456c055d",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "column.shape"
      ],
      "id": "145261b9",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row = data[np.newaxis, :]\n",
        "row"
      ],
      "id": "c54bfbe5",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row.shape"
      ],
      "id": "6ee15886",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {},
      "source": [
        "row[0, 0] = -1\n",
        "data"
      ],
      "id": "0874cf2b",
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
